Support v2 (#3911)

* Support v2

This adds support for linkerd v2, with the mapping of the new metrics,
and keeping the old ones around for compatibility purposes.

It changes `metric_to_check` to be a value reported by both versions.

* Update metadata

* Don't override service_check as it can be disabled.

* Split sum and count values in metadata
